类 AdvancedArchiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • AdvancedArchiver

  • public class AdvancedArchiver
extends java.lang.Object
    A small utility that creates a zip file off of the entire project directory, erasing the .git and doc directories which might make the submission too heavy for submit.cs. erasing the .git directory which might make the submission too heavy for submit.cs. Execute as Java application. Tested on Eclipse and IntelliJ.

    Do not edit this file! It is provided to you as a script that you should run as a Java application from your IDE every time you want to submit your project.
